items.name: vimprobable
items.description: Vimprobable is a web browser that behaves like the Vimperator plugin available for Mozilla Firefox. It is based on the WebKit engine (using GTK bindings). The goal of Vimprobable is to build a completely keyboard-driven, efficient and pleasurable browsing-experience. Its featureset might be considered "minimalistic", but not as minimalistic as being completely featureless.
